00w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/black-eyed-peas-unicorn-lawsuit-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/black-eyed-peas-unicorn-lawsuit-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/black-eyed-peas-unicorn-lawsuit-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一款会便便的独角兽玩具的制造商已与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-eyed-peas">黑眼豆豆</a>就模仿“我的驼峰”一事达成和解。</p><p>今年 1 月，黑眼豆豆的音乐发行商 BMG 版权管理公司对 MGA（Bratz 背后的公司）采取了法律行动， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-eyed-peas-sue-toy-company-over-singing-pooping-unicorn-3384875">理由是他们 2005 年的歌曲与 Poopsie Slime Surprise: Dancing Unicorn 玩具所演唱的歌曲有相似之处</a>。</p><p>根据诉讼称，这些玩具在按下其心形肚脐时会唱出一首名为“我的便便”的歌曲。然而，据称这首歌抄袭了说唱乐队 2005 年的热门单曲“My Humps”。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/business/legal/my-poops-song-lawsuit-settlement-my-humps-black-eyed-peas-1235432752/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Billboard</a></em>报道，现在，据报道双方已达成“原则和解”以解决诉讼。 </p><figure id="attachment_3511657" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3511657" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3511657" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/black-eyed-peas-2009.jpg" alt="黑眼豆豆" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/black-eyed-peas-2009.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/black-eyed-peas-2009-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/black-eyed-peas-2009-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/black-eyed-peas-2009-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/black-eyed-peas-2009-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/black-eyed-peas-2009-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3511657" class="wp-caption-text">加利福尼亚州洛杉矶 – CIRCA 2009：加利福尼亚州洛杉矶的黑眼豆豆（摄影：Aaron Rapoport/Corbis/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>在一月份提出的最初投诉中，BMG 表示，除了复制音乐元素之外，这首独角兽歌曲的主唱与黑眼豆豆乐队的 Fergie“听起来非常相似”。</p><p> “<em>我的便便，我的便便，我的便便，我的便便。那些粪便怎么办，那些粪便</em>，”玩具唱道。</p><p> “<em>我让我的父母发疯，我每天都这样做</em>，”它继续说道。在《我的驼峰》中，黑眼豆豆的菲姬唱道：“<em>我让这些兄弟发疯，我每天都这么做</em>。”</p><p> BMG 在诉讼中写道：“音乐，尤其是像《My Humps》这样的热门歌曲，在融入产品或在视频广告中使用时会增加巨大的价值，因为它提高了消费者的认知度、消费者的参与度和对产品的关注度。” “该侵权作品与《我的驼峰》极其相似，很明显该侵权作品是故意抄袭的。”</p><p>最近其他备受瞩目的版权案件中，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-wins-levitating-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-3452379">Dua Lipa</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-discusses-copyright-trial-in-new-tv-interview-i-have-not-done-something-wrong-3440503">Ed Sheeran</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/the-weeknd-settles-call-out-my-name-copyright-infringement-case-3416290">The Weeknd</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/taylor-swift-addresses-shake-it-off-copyright-lawsuit-the-lyrics-were-written-entirely-by-me-3286066">Taylor Swift</a>在内的艺术家也卷入了自己的法律纠纷。</p><p>另一方面，去年<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-i-am">Will.i.am</a>告诉<em>NME</em> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/will-i-am-and-james-bks-interview-black-eyed-peas-africa-manu-dibango-3278831">他正在制作一张新的 Black Eye Peas 专辑</a>。 “过去几个月我们一直在积极努力，并在路上不断录制，”他说。</p><p>七月，他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/britney-spears">布兰妮·斯皮尔斯</a>合作创作了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/britney-spears-and-will-i-am-team-up-on-clubby-new-single-mind-your-business-3471513">新歌“Mind Your Business”</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pooping-unicorn-toymaker-settles-black-eyed-peas-my-humps-parody-lawsuit-3511627">Pooping Unicorn 玩具制造商就黑眼豆豆的“我的驼峰”模仿诉讼达成和解，该诉讼</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
